            <scopecontent id="aspace_8aacd22d0200581593afef35b76f85c1">
               <head>Scope and Contents</head>
               <p>Within the "[?] at the Brick House" folder are a set of personal photographs from Duncan Robinson that features a group trip to Paul Mellon's home in Upperville, Virgina, known as the Brick House.  The horses folder features images of Mellon's various race horses, including a copy photo of Queen Elizabeth II with Mill Reef.  There are additional portraits of Mellon.</p>
            </scopecontent>
